tags: his tweet and stories made me cry
summary:
dan still advocating for mental health while he’s on break taking care of himself has me very emotional.
he cares so much for...
body:
dan still advocating for mental health while he’s on break taking care of himself has me very emotional.

he cares so much for his fan base. he could be using his platform to start drama or something else chaotic like many other highly influential people sadly do, but instead he’s out there letting people know that there’s nothing wrong with getting help.

he just wants everyone to be safe and okay.

there aren’t words to express my gratitude for all he’s done and continues to do or for how much i love him.

The first thing he does when he comes back is make a post about mental health and how it should...
body:
I have so, so much love for Dan

The first thing he does when he comes back is make a post about mental health and how it should school’s top priority because it would help so many people and he wants it to help people, especially since it did not help him. He has such a big heart and so much kindness and love to give the world, he really truly wants to help people in whatever way he can. Man, I really did miss him and this is the sweetest possible way for him to return
